Actress Nice Githinji is in mourning following the sudden death of her elder and only brother George Githinji.Speaking to Word Is on the phone, the talented thespian, who dabbles as a karaoke hostess, said her beloved brother died on Tuesday, April 11, after a long battle with illness.She said George sustained a serious injury on his head almost six years ago but his family didn't think that it would result in death.&ldquo;You know how people get sick and things just happen. So George was rushed to hospital and he died after two weeks,&rdquo; Nice said.Nice went on to reveal that his death came as a shock since she had just buried her nephew the previous week. George will be laid to rest on Thursday, April 20, in Kirinyaga.